OL,3,CWorld Cup hopes shattered for Wales
OL,4,Cand Ireland after agonising defeats
OL,6,FWales and Republic of Ireland suffered
OL,7,Fpenalty shout-out heartache dashing
OL,8,Ftheir dreams of qualifying for this
OL,9,Fsummer's FIFA World Cup.
OL,11,FCraig Bellamy's Wales were minutes
OL,12,Faway from making history in Cardiff
OL,13,Fafter Dan James' 51st-minute goal put
OL,14,Fthem ahead, but ex-Manchester City
OL,15,Fforward Edin Dzeko evened the score
OL,16,Fwith four minutes left before extra
OL,17,Ftime passed without a winner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
