OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774598699
OL,3,CWorld Cup hopes shattered for Wales
OL,4,Cand Ireland after agonising defeats
OL,6,FIt was initially first blood to Wales
OL,7,Fin the shoot-out after Karl Darlow
OL,8,Fdenied Ermedin Demirovic, but
OL,9,Fcelebrations were short-lived after
OL,10,FBrennan Johnson lifted his effort over
OL,11,Fand Neco Williams was denied to stun
OL,12,FCardiff City Stadium and give Bosnia a
OL,13,F4-2 win on penalties.
OL,15,FBosnia will face Italy on Thursday in
OL,16,Fa World Cup play-off to reach the
OL,17,Fsummer tournament in America.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
