OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774598699
OL,3,CWorld Cup hopes shattered for Wales
OL,4,Cand Ireland after agonising defeats
OL,6,FItaly got the better of Northern
OL,7,FIreland after Newcastle midfielder
OL,8,FSandro Tonali and Moise Kean struck in
OL,9,Fthe second half to secure a 2-0 win.
OL,11,FRepublic of Ireland's miraculous World
OL,12,FCup recovery almost pulled off another
OL,13,Foutstanding result, but much to their
OL,14,Ffans' anguish, they let a two-goal
OL,15,Flead slip in the Czech Republic before
OL,16,Fthey suffered a 4-3 defeat on
OL,17,Fpenalties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
