OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774598699
OL,3,CWorld Cup hopes shattered for Wales
OL,4,Cand Ireland after agonising defeats
OL,6,FTroy Parrott's 19th-minute spot-kick
OL,7,Fwas followed by a Matej Kovar own goal
OL,8,Ffour minutes later, but Patrik
OL,9,FSchick's penalty before half-time set
OL,10,Fup a tense second 45.
OL,12,FThe Czechs pushed for an equaliser and
OL,13,Fit arrived after 86 minutes when
OL,14,FLadislav Krejci found the net before
OL,15,Fspot-kicks were required to decide who
OL,16,Fwould face Denmark after they thrashed
OL,17,FNorth Macedonia 4-0 in their play-off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
