OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774598699
OL,3,CWorld Cup hopes shattered for Wales
OL,4,Cand Ireland after agonising defeats
OL,6,FIreland momentarily went ahead giving
OL,7,Fhope to fans, but that was short-lived
OL,8,Fas Finn Azaz and Alan Browne failed to
OL,9,Fscore from 12 yards and Heimir
OL,10,FHallgrimsson's team missed out on a
OL,11,Fplace at the World Cup after a 4-3
OL,12,Fshoot-out loss.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
